}
public static int randomlottery[] = {15000, 15001, 15002, 15003, 15004, 15005, 15006, 15007, 15008, 15009, 15010, 15011, 15012, 15013, 15014, 15015, 15016, 15017, 15018, 15019, 15020, 11694};
  public static int randomlottery() {
    return randomlottery[(int) (Math.random() * randomlottery.length)];
}[/code]
Change the randomlottery[] those numbers Example:15000, 15001, and stuff those are all dwarf remains, it means you lost the lottery.
